British Prime Minister David Cameron attends the cabal proceedings this evening and former CIA Director David Petraeus presents details on the "big data" spy grid which is set to become the new frontier of clandestine statecraft as internet connectivity becomes ubiquitous. 

David Knight hosts the show from Austin, Texas and author and presenter David Icke provides analysis and covers the unfolding events with Alex and crew as the Bilderberg confab enters its second day.
